<TR><TD>The Program</TD><TD>(#364-M01)</TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT>$89.95</TD></TR>
<TR><TD>Additional Facilitator's Guides</TD><TD>(#364-FG)</TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT>Each $3.50</TD></TR>
