<HEAD>
<TITLE>Corporate Profile--Agency Growth</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/images/backgrnd.jpg" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="FF00FF" ALINK="FF0000">
<TABLE WIDTH="100%">
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=40><IMG SRC="/images/bgspace.gif" BORDER=0 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=0></TD><TD>

<A HREF="/ait/aait.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/aitlogo.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HSPACE=0></A>

<H1><I>Corporate Profile&#151;</I></H1>
<HR>
<H1 align=center><I>Agency Growth</I></H1>
<BR>

<TABLE width="20%" align=right border cellpadding=10>
<TR><TD align=center><FONT color="780000"><B>
Leaders in the industry<HR width=50>
Efficient distribution<HR width=50>
New working partnerships<HR width=50>
Cooperation & collaboration<HR width=50>
Technology-based resources<HR width=50>
Innovations in curriculum
</B></FONT></TD></TR>
</TABLE>

<P><IMG SRC="drop_s.gif" ALIGN=LEFT>ince the 1960s, AIT has played a pivotal role in bringing together advanced technology and applied education, and there has been a steady increase in the need for our products and services.  Today, AIT&#146;s educational series are used on six continents and reach nearly thirty-four million students in North American classrooms each year via broadcast.  Our programs account for forty percent of the National Instructional Satellite Service schedule, which is broadcast to K&#150;12 classrooms in the United States.  AIT programs have been translated for use in Spanish and German.  We have series in American Sign Language and many series that are closed captioned.</P>

<P>AIT&#146;s growth was particularly strong in the first half of the 1990s.  During that time, we established important new working partnerships with organizations such as Phi Delta Kappa and South-Western Educational Publishing.  We made significant advances in the use of instructional tools such as computer programs and interactive videodiscs.  And we  improved our ability to produce and deliver quality educational resources rapidly and economically.</P>

<P>The result was a significant increase in business activity and a substantial improvement in our fiscal strength.  AIT has also constructed  a new corporate headquarters in Bloomington and we are completing our second year in that facility.  One of its main purposes is to provide additional space for our computerized distribution center.  It  also significantly increased our video editing and production capabilities.   These improvements and our recently expanded sales force will help ensure both AIT&#146;s future growth and our ability to provide faster, more efficient service to schools and school districts around the world.</P>


<TABLE align=right>
<TR><TD>
<IMG SRC="/profile/ag_blbox.gif"><IMG SRC="/profile/artrend.jpg">
</TD></TR>
</TABLE>
<BR clear=right>

