<H1>Performance Support Workshops</H1>
<H2>Regional Workshop Registration</H2>
<HR>


<P><IMG SRC="/images/workicon.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE=5>
All regional workshops will be conducted at AIT Headquarters, 1800 N. Stonelake Drive, Bloomington, Indiana.  The workshop fee is $250 for a two day workshop, and $125 for a one day workshop.  You will be responsible for your own transportation, lodging, and meals.</P>

<P>We have arranged with a nearby hotel to offer a special room rate of $40/night which includes a continental breakfast.  Indianapolis, 50 miles north, is the closest airport.  There is a shuttle bus available which will take you directly to the hotel for $30 round trip.  Transportation to and from the workshop will be provided.</P>

<P><IMG SRC="/images/workicon.gif" ALIGN=LEFT HSPACE=5>
To hold your place in one of the workshops listed below, fill out the registration form.  If you have any questions, please contact Mary Jane Lipp, at AIT Performance Support Workshops, <NOBR>(800) 457-4509,</NOBR> <NOBR>ext. 255</NOBR> or E-mail at <A HREF="MAILTO:mjlipp@ait.net">mjlipp@ait.net</A>.</P>
