<H1>Add it up:</H1>
<P>
<A HREF="/catalog/catpages/c372.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/prodlogo/372slogo.gif" ALIGN=LEFT><BR>
<H2><I>Mathemedia</I></A> fosters SCANS skills</H2>
<P>Add <I><A HREF="/catalog/catpages/c372.htm">Mathemedia</A> </I>to your curriculum and your 7th- through 12th-grade students will learn vital workplace skills as they master pre-algebra mathematics. The real-world examples in <I><A HREF="/catalog/catpages/c372.htm">Mathemedia</A> </I>are designed to help your students master the five competencies that are the foundation of successful job performance: effective use of resources, interpersonal skills, information, systems, and technology.
<P> The following chart correlates the 12 modules in <I><A HREF="/catalog/catpages/c372.htm">Mathemedia</A> </I>to the five competencies identified by the Secretary's Commission on Achieving Necessary Skills (SCANS) in <I>What Work Requires of Schools: A SCANS Report for America 2000.</I>
