<TITLE>AIT.NET ADDLINK</TITLE>
</HEAD>

<BODY BACKGROUND="/images/backgrnd.jpg" TEXT="000000" LINK="0000FF" VLINK="FF00FF" ALINK="FF0000">
<TABLE WIDTH="100%">
<TR><TD VALIGN=TOP WIDTH=40><IMG SRC="/images/bgspace.gif" BORDER=0 HSPACE=0 VSPACE=0></TD><TD>
<A HREF="/ait/aait.htm"><IMG SRC="/images/aitlogo.gif" ALIGN=RIGHT BORDER=0 HSPACE=0></A>
<H1>SUGGEST A LINK!</H1>

<P>In the near future, <B>AIT.Net</B> will automate the process for your submission of web sites that you have found informative, helpful, thought-provoking, or just fun.  Your suggestions will be added regularly to a list that will be generated by AIT staff, and by people who, like you, visit our site.

Until this page is fully constructed, submit your suggestions to <A HREF="MAILTO: ait@ait.net"><B>AIT.</B></A>  Please include the URL, and a brief description of the contents of the site.  Thanks!  
