␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!construction and operation of technologies.␀!<P>␀␀	␀␀␀␀␀␀ ␀␀␀␀␀␀␀
␀␀␀␀ ␀␀,␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀,␀␀8␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀8␀␀D␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!274-012 20minute video program $150␀!<P>␀␀
␀␀␀␀D␀␀P␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀P␀␀\␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀\␀␀h␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀h␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀]␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!"[You, Me, and Technology's] greatest strength is in the ways it engages␀␀␀␀Estudents in investigating trade-offs and choices that must be made when issues␀␀␀␀␀␀of lifestyle and human values conflict with technological potential . . . This␀␀␀perspective provides a healthy context for decision making."␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀t␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!41 XJ␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!Social Educational~␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!Textbook Correlation ~ ~4 ~ e␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀␀␀␀␀UU␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!Technology correlates with high school textbooks in Technology, Physics and␀␀␀␀UUPhysical Science, Biology, U.S. History, World History, Civics and Government,␀␀␀and Economics. (Textbook Correlation chart included in teacher's guide.)␀!<P>␀␀␀␀␀(␀␀L␀␀␀␀␀␀$␀␀␀␀L␀␀X␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀	␀␀␀␀'␀$␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!␀!<P>␀0␀␀␀␀X␀␀d␀␀␀␀␀␀X␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀	␀␀␀␀'␀0␀$␀ ␀␀␀d␀␀p␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀	␀␀␀␀'␀$␀␀!␀!␀␀␀␀Courier␀␀!␀!␀␀!#␀!Order Form␀!<P>␀0␀!␀␀␀p␀␀|␀␀␀␀␀␀p␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀	␀␀␀␀'␀0␀$␀"␀␀␀|␀␀␀␀␀␀'␀␀␀
