</TABLE><P>

Purchase <B>Before the Bell Rings</B> (#385-M01) for $295 and receive one 60-minute video program and one 32-page facilitator's guide in a vinyl album.<P>

<HR>
"As the roles of paraeducators have expanded and become more complex and challenging, their need for effective communication and problem solving skills has increased.  Before the Bell Rings meets these training needs."<P>

Anna Lou Pickett,<BR>
Chief Consultant,<BR>
Director of the National Resource Center for Paraprofessionals in Education and Related Services
