</TABLE><P>

<HR>
"The more instruments you have, the more beautiful the music . . . We should value 
the diversity we have as one of our biggest strengths."<P>

Elaine Griffin<BR> 
1995 National Teacher of the Year,<BR> 
Kodiak Island, Alaska
