http://www.ait.org:80/technos/new/bracey03.htm 206.106.95.11 19970113044131 text/html 6282
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 1997 05:37:04 GMT
Server: Microsoft-Internet-Information-Server/1.0
Content-Type: text/html
Last-Modified: Mon, 03 Jun 1996 21:03:35 GMT
