<IMG SRC="hamner.jpg" ALIGN=LEFT VSPACE="10" ALIGN=RIGHT HSPACE="10">
<BR><BR>
<H2 ALIGN=CENTER><I>Pat Hamner</I></H2>
<BR>
<HR>
<P>
Pat Hamner brings to AIT's Board of Directors both national and state experience as an education policy maker. She is a past President of the National Association of State Boards of Education (1992), a former member of the West Virginia State Board of Education (1982-1993) and has just finished the co-chairmanship for the West Virginia Education First Advisory Panel  (Goals 2000). Pat has a keen interest in how technology can be integrated into the public education system to provide skills and tools for lifelong learning.
</P>
<P ALIGN=CENTER>
Pat Hamner may be reached via email at <A HREF="MAILTO: hamner_p@academ.wvwc.edu"> hamner_p@academ.wvwc.edu</A>.
